Subject: [PATCH] media: imx-jpeg: Ensure power suppliers be suspended before
 detach them
References: bsc#1218260
Patch-mainline: 6.6.64
Git-commit: fd0af4cd35da0eb550ef682b71cda70a4e36f6b9

commit fd0af4cd35da0eb550ef682b71cda70a4e36f6b9 upstream.

